oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: George Jones, Tammy Wynette, and Patsy Sledd
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand Ole Opry (Radio program); Jones, George, 1931-2013; Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency; Morrison, Harold; Offset printing; Sledd, Patsy; Wynette, Tammy;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white negatives taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising Grand Ole Opry stars George Jones, Tammy Wynette, Patsy Sledd, Harold Morrison, Charlie Carter, James Hollie, and the Jones Boys, available through the Harry (Hap) Peebles Agency. The negative features photographs of George Jones, Tammy Wynette, Patsy Sledd, and Harold Morrison. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
